title: This Month's GTA+ Benefits
headline: This Month's GTA+ Benefits
subtitle: GTA+
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposited directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ members who've signed up for this month (May 2 - June 5) will also receive:

— An extra bonus of GTA$1,000,000 every month through August
— The Överflöd Entity MT
— The Classique Broadway
— The Albany Roosevelt
— Exclusive clothing
— 2X Rewards on A Superyacht Life Contact Missions
— And more

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel any time. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
